                          No agent activity yet. Seed the hive to populate this stream.
                        </li>
                      )}
                    </ul>
                  </div>

                  <div className="space-y-4 rounded-2xl border border-black/10 bg-white/80 p-5 dark:border-white/10 dark:bg-white/10">
